    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Deseed your <strong>red</strong> <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and dice</p><p>Peel and chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Slice your<strong> halloumi</strong> into 3 pieces per person</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
