    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> coriander</strong> finely (including the stalks)</p><p>Combine the<strong> chopped coriander</strong> and <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> in a small bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>coriander salsa</strong></p>",
